Package de.frauas.dronesimulation.app.dronetype

Class DroneType

java.lang.Object
de.frauas.dronesimulation.app.dronetype.DroneType
public class DroneType extends Object
This class represents a type of drone with various properties. drone type objects are created using droneTypeURI that is stored in each drone instane object and associated with the drone instance object. for every drone model there is only one drone type object.

  • Constructor Details

    • DroneType

      public DroneType(int _typeId, String _manufacturer, String _typeName, int _weight, int _maxSpeed, int _batteryCapacity, int _controlRange, int _maxCarriage)
      Constructs a new DroneType with the given parameters.
      Parameters:
      _typeId - the ID of the drone type (different from the drone ID in drone objects)
      _manufacturer - the manufacturer of the drone
      _typeName - the name of the drone type
      _weight - the weight of the drone
      _maxSpeed - the maximum speed of the drone
      _batteryCapacity - the battery capacity of the drone
      _controlRange - the control range of the drone
      _maxCarriage - the maximum carriage of the drone
